# --- ml weights ---
# Only the production checkpoint (best_model_v3.pth) is shipped, via Git LFS,
# so `docker compose up --build` works out of the box. Experimental v1/v2/v4
# and intermediate checkpoints are not distributed.
*.pth
!TechPackApp/techpack_generator/models/best_model_v3.pth
*.ckpt
*.bin
*.onnx
*.safetensors
TechPackApp/techpack_generator/models/checkpoints/

# --- training data (not pushed) ---
# Schema and a single tiny example are tracked so the data shape is clear;
# bulk training/validation corpora and intermediate checkpoints are not.
TechPackApp/techpack_generator/training_data/checkpoint_*.json
TechPackApp/techpack_generator/training_data/combined_train.json
TechPackApp/techpack_generator/training_data/combined_val.json
TechPackApp/techpack_generator/training_data/synthetic/

